things we don't know?

114
00:11:29.166 --> 00:11:31.040
How about the Internet?!

115
00:11:31.041 --> 00:11:34.874
I believe there's a computer
lab? - Yes.

116
00:11:34.875 --> 00:11:37.708
It's out of service at the
moment.

117
00:11:40.000 --> 00:11:41.207
Okay.

118
00:11:41.208 --> 00:11:44.208
Where else can we find answers?

119
00:11:46.750 --> 00:11:49.207
