162
00:14:17.083 --> 00:14:18.457
That's all?

163
00:14:18.458 --> 00:14:20.749
Fine, that's easy.

164
00:14:20.750 --> 00:14:24.957
As of now, you all get a 10.

165
00:14:24.958 --> 00:14:28.082
At the end of the year, when you
get your report cards, you're

166
00:14:28.083 --> 00:14:30.875
